{"type": "article", "id": 25007, "title": "瓶身像古典柱子一样的啤酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-06T07:19:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104129XFtUzWuf7P8MwLI4.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Noam 啤酒致力于重拾德国巴伐利亚啤酒口感，他们找到来自北欧的 Acne 设计包装。瓶身刻有一圈竖条状的凹槽，就像是古典圆柱上的样式，看起来更加细长，搭配黄色的啤酒后更显典雅珍贵。透过瓶子可以清晰看到气泡，而经过冰镇后的水珠则会顺着凹槽流下去，非常清爽。<a href=\"http://eyeondesign.aiga.org/happy-hour-clever-tactile-beer-wine-packaging/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104127GT4ztaEMsRnXdPH0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104128lvrPS6h4jtVZgCWG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104129PK3YhzDUTMIwobxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3725\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}